{"type":"message","id":"74ad4b5f","parentId":"7ce5d175","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:50:15.864Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 16:50:13 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b52bfd29aa4e4b36a53b745afaaf]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52bfd29aa4e4b36a53b745afaaf\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 16:50 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n不是，我重新配置了这个，先不用管了。\n\n然后是这样：\n1. 你的这个SOP存在哪个文件里？\n2. 在选品的时候，除了以图搜款以外，我们对价格上要有一个甄别。\n\n比如说我们要有一个范围，这个我们可能还需要再丰富一下"}],"timestamp":1775811015859}}
{"type":"message","id":"fde2b030","parentId":"74ad4b5f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:50:31.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking:\n1. Where is the SOP stored?\n2. When selecting products, besides image search on 1688, they need price filtering criteria - they want to establish a price range/criteria\n\nLet me answer:\n\n1. The SOP (selection process) is stored in SOUL.md - that's my core configuration file\n2. Price range/criteria for 1688 sourcing - they want to establish price thresholds\n\nLet me respond naturally."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 1. SOP 存在 `SOUL.md` 里，也就是我加载的那个文件。你可以直接编辑它来调整策略。\n\n2. 价格甄别的问题好，现在1688采购价大概是什么范围？我可以帮你定一个参考区间：\n\n- **发夹/头绳**：客单价低，1688采购价建议控制在 ¥2-8\n- **发箍**：¥3-15 左右\n- **抓夹**：¥5-20 左右\n- **发簪**：¥5-25 左右\n\n你觉得这个范围合理吗？或者你有一个具体的上限（比如采购价不超过 ¥30）？我们可以把它固化到 SOP 里。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775811015868,"responseId":"0627ecc80b6f350f6f99e8b8ae07f7de"}}
