{"type":"message","id":"6ee8bd6b","parentId":"e20506fb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:25:54.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good overview. Let me identify the most relevant Skills for the product selection workflow. The main steps are:\n\n1. 获取 TikTok Shop 热销/高增长商品数据\n2. 1688 以图搜款找货源\n3. 采集链接、价格、款式信息\n4. 录入飞书表格\n\nKey candidates:\n1. **douyin-tiktok-trends** - 获取 TikTok 趋势数据，可能有助于了解热销品类\n2. **1688-product-search** - 1688商品搜索，可能可以替代部分以图搜款\n\n\n3. **query-1688-product-detail** - 查询1688商品详情，对获取价格、重量等信息很有帮助\n4. **taobao-image-search** - 淘宝图片搜索，虽然主要面向国内但可能也适用于以图搜款\n5. **ecommerce-product-research** - 电商产品研究，覆盖面比较广\n6. **1688-sourcing** - 1688采购助手，可能对采购流程有帮助\n7. **ecommerce-product-picker** - 电商选品工具，可能与现有流程直接相关\n\n我应该进一步了解这些工具的具体功能，特别是它们能否帮助自动化当前的选品步骤。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3eeddc5ba4ef46c89fbb9772","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub info douyin-tiktok-trends 2>&1; echo \"===\"; clawhub info 1688-product-search 2>&1; echo \"===\"; clawhub info ecommerce-product-picker 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775831146144,"responseId":"06283b6ab50ee5045bc1e8d9d47af360"}}
