{"type":"message","id":"c63d9c79","parentId":"8e1ad52f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:27:13.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture of the available skills. Let me also check on the ecommerce-product-picker more closely since it mentions 小红书/TikTok 热度 + 精细利润计算 which is very relevant.\n\nLet me compile the list of skills I found that are most relevant for the HALEI's use case:\n\n**High Relevance:**\n1. **ecommerce-product-picker** - 跨境电商选品 AI 工具 v4，支持 TikTok/小红书热度 + 利润计算 + BSR 转换 + 平台热榜 - Very relevant!\n2. **douyin-tiktok-trends** - 抖音/TikTok 趋势获取，支持 trending topics/hashtags/songs/creators - Relevant for understanding trends\n\n\n3. **1688-product-search** - 1688商品搜索，支持关键词+图片搜索+商品详情，通过 1688 开放平台官方 API，提供完整的 1688 商品搜索能力\n4. **1688-sourcing** - 1688 采购助手，支持利润计算 + 多平台产品上架\n5. **taobao-image-search** - 淘宝以图搜同款，可用于 1688 以图搜款\n6. **query-1688-product-detail** - 1688 商品详情查询\n\n（通过 AlphaShop API）\n7. **ecommerce-product-research** - 使用 PipiAds 研究电商产品，支持 TikTok 和 Facebook 广告数据\n8. **ecommerce-analyzer** - 电商数据分析，支持多平台销售/价格/评论/关键词/竞争对手监控\n9. **1688-to-ozon** - 1688 商品自动采集并上传到 OZON 平台（改写后可用于 TikTok Shop）\n10. **cross-border-ecommerce-skill** - 跨境电商规划工具，支持市场选择、物流、支付、税务合规和本地化\n\nNow I should compile this list for HALEI and store it in memory."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ecd3612191e5431d94a2b7de","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect ecommerce-product-picker 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775831222119,"responseId":"06283bb606d93b2be2e9a884d8ae9e23"}}
