{"type":"message","id":"6ca4d6fe","parentId":"d65e8be8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T14:27:43.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I should send a summary message to HALEI about what I found."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 调研完成！从 clawhub 筛选出以下适合咱选品流程的 Skills：\n\n**🏆 核心推荐（可直接安装）**\n\n| Skill | 用途 |\n|-------|------|\n| **douyin-tiktok-trends** | TikTok/抖音趋势抓取，获取热搜话题、标签、达人 |\n| **ecommerce-product-picker** | 跨境选品工具，含实时趋势+TikTok热度+利润计算 |\n| **1688-product-search** | 1688官方API，支持关键词+图片搜索+商品详情 |\n| **taobao-image-search** | 淘宝以图搜款，可作为1688的备选方案 |\n\n这4个工具覆盖了选品流程中\"数据采集→以图搜款→1688详情\"的主要环节。\n\n**❌ 暂不推荐**：1688-to-ozon（面向OZON平台）、cross-border-ecommerce-skill（偏向物流合规，非选品数据）\n\n明天沟通确认两点：\n1. 是否安装这几个 Skills？\n2. `ecommerce-product-picker` 数据源是否覆盖泰国/越南 TikTok（需测试）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775831252727,"responseId":"06283bd5c7bc29cb5ffeadf887eb3ca1"}}
